Both sex workers and human rights groups like Amnesty International oppose this strategy.
Under the Nordic Model, sex workers are still subjected to police surveillance, stings, and raids meant to catch their customers.
Harris supported FOSTA and targeted Backpage, twice, but was stopped by a judge both times.
